  "title": "SENIOR TALENT ACQUISITION PARTNER, ASIA",
  "description": "<p>You’ll combine hands-on recruiting expertise with consultative guidance, shaping the way we connect with candidates and ensuring an exceptional experience every step of the way.</p><ul><li>Partner with leaders and HR Business Partners to understand hiring needs and craft effective recruiting strategies. </li><li>Manage the full recruitment cycle—from sourcing and screening through offers and onboarding—for corporate roles across Yum!’s brands. </li><li>Build diverse pipelines through creative sourcing, networking, and market research. </li><li>Deliver an outstanding candidate experience, ensuring every interaction reflects Yum!’s values. </li><li>Use data and metrics to track progress, share insights, and continuously improve how we hire. </li><li>Lead and contribute to projects that elevate our talent acquisition practices, from employer branding to process innovation. </li><li>Champion equity, inclusion, and belonging by embedding inclusive practices in every hiring process. </li></ul>",
